high_descs: Look up at the silver, circle towel rack on the left wall.
Take the towel from the rack.
Turn left and look down at the cabinet.
Open the cabinet door, place the towel inside, and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place the towel inside the cabinet below the sink.

high_descs: Face the mirror at the top of the sink
Grab the towel on the left side of the sink
Turn to the cabinet under the sink
Open the cabinet and put the towel in the cabinet, close the door
anns.task_desc: Get the towel, put it in the cabinet under the sink

high_descs: Look down to the floor and then back up.
Grab the towel on the rack.
Open the cabinet and put the towel in it.
anns.task_desc: Move the towel from the rack to the cabinet under the sink.
